<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="kindness-n">kindness <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kaɪndnəs/    美 /'kaɪndnəs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 仁慈；和蔼；好意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>out of kindness 
出于好心</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>with kindness 
亲切地</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She kept thanking me for my kindness.
她不停地感谢我的好意。</p><footer>2008 北京</footer></div>

<h4 id="2c">2.<strong>[C] 好心的行为；好事； (一番) 好意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Will you <strong>do me a kindness</strong>? 
你能帮帮我吗?</p></div></div>